00:23:49.170 --> 00:23:53.300
and with the single weapon of acrucifix, converted them.

235
00:23:53.300 --> 00:23:56.400
And they built this church.

236
00:23:56.400 --> 00:24:00.830
It was not possible to bury thedead in the solid stone.

