00:24:22.470 --> 00:24:26.870
it's not surprising that thereare hardly any trace of theSpanish marches.

241
00:24:26.870 --> 00:24:33.800
But there's an amazing one. Itis this towering bluff, ElMorro.

242
00:24:33.800 --> 00:24:38.570
Indian guides led Coronado to itwhen his men were fainting withthirst.

243
00:24:38.570 --> 00:24:42.170
At the foot of it was this poolof pure water,

244
00:24:42.170 --> 00:24:45.000
which is something that anywherein the arid West

