00:40:35.300 --> 00:40:40.300
who had beaten their ancestorsinto a new, bizarre religion.

400
00:41:49.800 --> 00:41:52.530
Neither the plundering life ofthe Conquistadors

401
00:41:52.530 --> 00:41:56.500
nor the vigorous life of theranchers went on for ever.

402
00:41:56.500 --> 00:42:01.230
As time went on so did themellowing of the Spanishheritage,

403
00:42:01.230 --> 00:42:06.170
till by the beginning of the19th century the Spanish werethoroughly domesticated

404
00:42:06.170 --> 00:42:09.670
in this part of the world, andespecially here in California.

405
00:42:09.670 --> 00:42:13.700
By now the Indians had beentrained to be carpenters

406
00:42:13.700 --> 00:42:18.200
and farmers and blacksmiths andgrowers of vines.

407
00:42:18.200 --> 00:42:21.830
And comfortable families notmuch interested in money,

408
00:42:21.830 --> 00:42:26.430
raised enough cattle and enoughcrops for their needs,

409
00:42:26.430 --> 00:42:31.130
practiced a strict butaffectionate Catholic disciplineon their children,

410
00:42:31.130 --> 00:42:38.800
and lived in squares like these,lives that were balanced anduseful and benevolent.

411
00:42:50.770 --> 00:42:55.830
The Spaniards' imperialambitions were checkmated toosoon for them to build,

412
00:42:55.830 --> 00:43:02.000
as the French did here in NewOrleans, a full-blown capitalcity.

413
00:43:02.000 --> 00:43:04.230
This might have been the capitalof the United States

414
00:43:04.230 --> 00:43:10.700
if Napoleon had not sold forcash the huge interior which LaSalle had claimed as Louisiana.

415
00:43:10.700 --> 00:43:14.730
But the French and then theSpanish prospered here, lawyersand bankers, merchants,

416
00:43:14.730 --> 00:43:16.400
ambassadors and playboys,

417
00:43:16.400 --> 00:43:19.800
maintaining their quadroonmistresses in terracedapartments

418
00:43:19.800 --> 00:43:21.800
overlooking the main square.

419
00:43:42.370 --> 00:43:46.700
Today New Orleans more or lessincorporates as a touristpackage

420
00:43:46.700 --> 00:43:48.570
the French heritage in theUnited States.

421
00:43:48.570 --> 00:43:54.570
And it is practically anobligation to abjure the hot dogfor the snail.

