433
00:44:57.400 --> 00:45:01.130
They are recognized only as thenames of automobiles.

434
00:45:01.130 --> 00:45:05.330
But in these quiet patios I'mreminded of one grand exception,

435
00:45:05.330 --> 00:45:10.470
